        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHPdS",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:04:50Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:04:50Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 7,
              "body": "I would use this references for \"X-Wing algorithms\" instead of IANA.\r\n\r\nhttps://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem/",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:04:50Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:04:50Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHQWH",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:06:08Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:06:08Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 17,
              "body": "Here you should say the algorithm registered in this document.\r\nI do not think you need to leave room for IANA to register other X-Wings, but perhaps that is a consideration",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:06:08Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:06:08Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHRzf",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:08:17Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:08:18Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 20,
              "body": "AKP is a new key type that is like OKP, but does not require curve.\r\n\r\nThe spec that defines the \"alg\" can be as specific about \"pub\" and \"priv\" as you want it to be.\r\nI recommend citing https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem-06#name-key-generation\r\n\r\nAnd stating that \"pub\" is concat(pk_M, pk_X)\r\n\r\nIn the case of JWK, this value is base64url encoded.",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:08:17Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:08:18Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHTMZ",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:10:07Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:10:07Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 23,
              "body": "I think priv here, should be `sk` (the seed) used to derive ML-KEM and X25519 private keys, as described in the same section I noted above, for example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nGenerateKeyPair() returns the 32 byte secret decapsulation key sk\r\n```",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:10:07Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:10:07Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHT2v",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:11:22Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:11:22Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 32,
              "body": "This example is lacking quotes on the JSON keys, and the specific algorithm is subject to change probably.\r\nAlso JSON does not support comments",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:11:22Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:11:22Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UHUfQ",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "OR13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "state": "APPROVED",
          "body": "With some nits, but I think this is a step in a good direction",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T14:12:04Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T14:12:04Z",
          "comments": []
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UJ9UX",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "ilaril",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T18:51:31Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T18:51:31Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 20,
              "body": "Section 5.8.2. of draft-connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem-06 says:\r\n\r\n\"The publicKey component MUST be absent.\" (in private keys). That requirement is there for security reasons (as some stated security properties fail otherwise). Unfortunately, \"AKP\" does not allow omitting the public key.\r\n\r\nAnd \"pub\" is X-Wing encapsulation key (as defined by draft-connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem-06). That is 1216 bytes. Treating the value as any sort of concatenation is asking for trouble.",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T18:51:31Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T19:03:03Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UJ-tY",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "ilaril",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-06T18:54:53Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T18:54:54Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 23,
              "body": "\"priv\" is X-Wing decapsulation key (as defined by draft-connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem-06). That is 32-bytes.",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-06T18:54:54Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-06T18:54:54Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOLfqsKc6UKBx7",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "dce85ae"
          },
          "author": "ilaril",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
