          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 23,
              "body": "```suggestion\r\n  When representing an X-Wing private key, the private key parameter MUST be present and MUST contain the X-Wing decapsulation key (sk) as defined in Section 5.2 of {{?I-D.connolly-cfrg-xwing-kem}}. When represented as a JWK, this value MUST be base64url-encoded. \r\n```",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-09T20:55:31Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-09T20:55:31Z"
            }
